*******************************************************************************
       Name: Seal Calculus
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 25
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: !Seal Calculus!
Acquisition:
   - Cleric: level 79
Description:
   Seal Calculus is a high-level Cleric utility spell that performs a
   comprehensive divine calculation of all seals and testimonies present in
   an area. The spell evaluates the spiritual state of the environment,
   counting and categorizing active divine seals, testimonies, and ledger
   marks, and reveals information about their strength and who placed them.

   For Clerics who work extensively with the Pale Ledger's sealing system,
   Seal Calculus is an invaluable administrative tool. It allows a senior
   Cleric to audit the divine accounting of an area and identify any seals
   that have been tampered with, weakened, or improperly placed. The spell
   is rarely used in combat but is essential for advanced work with Disk's
   judicial and archival systems.
*******************************************************************************
